io.github.u004.slf4jext

Class Log

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.u004.slf4jext.Log

  • public final class Log
extends Object
    A logging utility.

    Log is the utility class that wraps Logger and all the methods with automatic type detection of the calling Class, so you do not need to pre-define a static constant of the Logger instance from LoggerFactory.

    Since:
    2.0.3
